---
title: Bulgogi Style Lamb with Roasted Broccoli, Mushrooms and Jasmine Rice
description: We love a Bulgogi Style Lamb and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/bulgogi-style-lamb-5ef15b70-4050fa3c.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/bulgogi-style-lamb-5d3ac6a6769619000a461975-942678ce.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/bulgogi-style-lamb-5d3ac6a6769619000a461975
